WEBVTT

00:03.521 --> 00:06.258
Taking a break can mean so many different things.

00:07.805 --> 00:09.047
It's a moment to relax,...

00:12.845 --> 00:14.065
...a moment to reflect,...

00:15.149 --> 00:16.076
...a moment to fly...

00:18.513 --> 00:19.940
...or a moment to set sail.

00:26.174 --> 00:28.797
Nevertheless, it's simply a moment,...

00:32.614 --> 00:36.739
...and when the moment comes, we will be here.

